    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<font size="5">Markdown 语法</font>  <p>注意：为了方便记忆，同样功能的语法只选较为简单的介绍。本文力求语法功能的多样性！</p><h2 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h2><p>在行首插入 1 到 6 个 # ，对应到标题 1 到 6 阶，例如：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 这是 H1</span><br><span class="line">## 这是 H2</span><br><span class="line">###### 这是 H6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="换行"><a href="#换行" class="headerlink" title="换行"></a>换行</h2><ol><li>连续两个以上空格+回车</li><li>使用html语言换行标签：<code>&lt;br&gt;</code></li></ol><h2 id="字体字号颜色"><a href="#字体字号颜色" class="headerlink" title="字体字号颜色"></a>字体字号颜色</h2><p>markdown 也是支持内嵌 HTML 标签的。<br>因此可以表示为<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;font face=&quot;微软雅黑&quot;&gt;我是微软雅黑&lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font color=&quot;#0099ff&quot; size=&quot;7&quot; face=&quot;黑体&quot;&gt;color=#0099ff size=72 face=&quot;黑体&quot;&lt;/font&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>size可选1-7，其中1最小，7最大。markdown默认的字号好像是3  </p><h2 id="修辞和强调"><a href="#修辞和强调" class="headerlink" title="修辞和强调"></a>修辞和强调</h2><p>Markdown 使用星号和底线来标记需要强调的区段。<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Some of these words *are emphasized*.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Some of these words _are emphasized also_.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Use two asterisks for **strong emphasis**.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Or, if you prefer, __use two underscores instead__.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>效果如下：<br>Some of these words <em>are emphasized</em>.</p><p>Some of these words <em>are emphasized also</em>.</p><p>Use two asterisks for <strong>strong emphasis</strong>.</p><p>Or, if you prefer, <strong>use two underscores instead</strong>.</p><p>如果你的 * 和 _ 两边都有空白的话，它们就只会被当成普通的符号。  </p><h2 id="反斜杠"><a href="#反斜杠" class="headerlink" title="反斜杠"></a>反斜杠</h2><p>Markdown 可以利用反斜杠来插入一些在语法中有其它意义的符号，例如：如果你想要用星号加在文字旁边的方式来做出强调效果，你可以在星号的前面加上反斜杠：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\*literal asterisks\*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>Markdown 支持以下这些符号前面加上反斜杠来帮助插入普通的符号：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\\   反斜线</span><br><span class="line">\`   反引号</span><br><span class="line">\*   星号</span><br><span class="line">\_    底线</span><br><span class="line">\&#123;&#125;  花括号</span><br><span class="line">\[]  方括号</span><br><span class="line">\()  括弧</span><br><span class="line">\#   井字号</span><br><span class="line">\+   加号</span><br><span class="line">\-   减号</span><br><span class="line">\.   英文句点</span><br><span class="line">\!   惊叹号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="分隔线"><a href="#分隔线" class="headerlink" title="分隔线"></a>分隔线</h2><p>你可以在一行中用三个以上的星号、减号、底线来建立一个分隔线，行内不能有其他东西。你也可以在星号或是减号中间插入空格。下面每种写法都可以建立分隔线：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">* * *</span><br><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">*****</span><br><span class="line">- - -</span><br><span class="line">---------------------------------------</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h2><p>无序列表使用<strong>星号、加号和减号</strong>来做为列表的项目标记，<strong>项目标记后面则一定要接着至少一个空格或制表符。</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">* Candy.</span><br><span class="line">+ Gum.</span><br><span class="line">- Booze.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><ul><li>Candy.</li></ul><ul><li>Gum.</li></ul><ul><li>Booze.</li></ul><p>有序的列表则是使用一般的数字接着一个英文句点作为项目标记：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. Red</span><br><span class="line">2. Green</span><br><span class="line">3. Blue</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>在一个项目内放上<strong>多个段落</strong>，只要在它前面缩排4个空白或1个tab。<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">* A list item.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    With multiple paragraphs.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    Another item in the list.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>在列表项目内放进<strong>引用</strong>，那 <code>&gt;</code> 就需要缩排4个空白或2个tab：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*   A list item with a block quote:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &gt; This is a block quote</span><br><span class="line">    &gt; inside a list item.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>在列表项目内放<strong>代码区块</strong>，该区块就需要缩进两次，也就是8个空格或是4个制表符：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*   一列表项包含一个列表区块：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        &lt;代码写在这&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><p>在一般的段落文字中，你可以使用反引号`来标记代码区段</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">I wish SmartyPants used named entities like `&amp;mdash;`</span><br><span class="line">instead of decimal-encoded entites like `&amp;#8212;`.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>I wish SmartyPants used named entities like <code>&amp;mdash;</code><br>instead of decimal-encoded entites like <code>&amp;#8212;</code>.  </p><h2 id="代码区块"><a href="#代码区块" class="headerlink" title="代码区块"></a>代码区块</h2><p>如果要建立一个已经格式化好的代码区块，只要每行都缩进 4 个空格或是2个 tab 就可以了<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是一个普通段落：</span><br><span class="line">    这是一个代码区块。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>代码区块的效果如下：</p><pre><code>这是一个代码区块。</code></pre><p><strong>一个代码区块会一直持续到没有缩进的那一行（或是文件结尾）。</strong></p><p>代码区块中，一般的 Markdown 语法不会被转换  </p><hr><p>但是这样做出来的代码区块没有很好看，我查看了hexo中的例子，发现例子中并没有用4个空格或者2个tab的方式来做出代码区块，而是用一下三个反引号！如下：</p><blockquote><p>```<br>引用的文字<br>```</p></blockquote><p>如果用了三个反引号，那么引用部分每行前面是有数字的，但是如果用的是四个空格或者两个tab，则是没有数字的，就没有那么好看了。</p><h2 id="区块引用"><a href="#区块引用" class="headerlink" title="区块引用"></a>区块引用</h2><p> 文件中建立一个区块引用，那会看起来像是你自己先断好行，然后在每行的最前面加上>:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; ## 这是一个标题。</span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt; 1.   这是第一行列表项。</span><br><span class="line">&gt; 2.   这是第二行列表项。</span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt; &gt;给出一些例子代码：</span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;     return shell_exec(&quot;echo $input | $markdown_script&quot;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><h2 id="这是一个标题。"><a href="#这是一个标题。" class="headerlink" title="这是一个标题。"></a>这是一个标题。</h2><ol><li>这是第一行列表项。</li><li>这是第二行列表项。</li></ol><blockquote><p>给出一些例子代码：</p></blockquote><pre><code>return shell_exec(&quot;echo $input | $markdown_script&quot;);</code></pre></blockquote><p>引用的区块内也可以使用其他的 Markdown 语法，包括标题、列表、代码区块等，并且可以嵌套。</p><p>Markdown 也允许你偷懒只在整个段落的第一行最前面加上 &gt; （PS回车一次和加了空格的效果是一样的，依然是一段！回车两次那就真的分行了）：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; This is a block quote with two paragraphs. Lorem ipsum dolor sitamet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aliquam hendrerit mi posuere lectus.</span><br><span class="line">Vestibulum enim wisi, viverra nec, fringilla in, laoreet vitae, risus.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><blockquote><p>This is a block quote with two paragraphs. Lorem ipsum dolor sitamet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aliquam hendrerit mi posuere lectus.<br>Vestibulum enim wisi, viverra nec, fringilla in, laoreet vitae, risus. </p></blockquote><h2 id="自动链接"><a href="#自动链接" class="headerlink" title="自动链接"></a>自动链接</h2><p>Markdown 支持以比较简短的自动链接形式来处理网址和电子邮件信箱，只要是用尖括号包起来，例如：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;http://example.com/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;address@example.com&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">This is an [example link](http://example.com/).</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">I get 10 times more traffic from [Google][1] than from</span><br><span class="line">[Yahoo][2] or [MSN][3].</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[1]: http://google.com/ &quot;Google&quot;</span><br><span class="line">[2]: http://search.yahoo.com/ &apos;Yahoo Search&apos;</span><br><span class="line">[3]: http://search.msn.com/ (MSN Search)</span><br><span class="line">[id]: &lt;http://example.com/&gt;  &quot;Optional Title Here&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>This is an <a href="http://example.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">example link</a>.<br>I get 10 times more traffic from <a href="http://google.com/" title="Google" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google</a> than from<br><a href="http://search.yahoo.com/" title="Yahoo Search" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yahoo</a> or <a href="http://search.msn.com/" title="MSN Search" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MSN</a>.</p><hr><p>可以在文件的任意地方（并不仅限于文末，文中也行）定义该链接的内容：</p><p>title 内容，可以用单引号、双引号或是括弧包着。也可以把 title 放到下一行，也可以加一些缩进，若网址太长的话，这样会比较好看</p><p>以下两种方式也行：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. I get 10 times more traffic from [Google][] than from [Yahoo][] or [MSN][].</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  [google]: http://google.com/        &quot;Google&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  [yahoo]:  http://search.yahoo.com/  &quot;Yahoo Search&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  [msn]:    http://search.msn.com/    &quot;MSN Search&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">2. I get 10 times more traffic from [Google](http://google.com/ &quot;Google&quot;) than from [Yahoo](http://search.yahoo.com/ &quot;Yahoo Search&quot;) or [MSN](http://search.msn.com/ &quot;MSN Search&quot;).</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><ol><li>I get 10 times more traffic from <a href="http://google.com/" title="Google" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google</a> than from <a href="http://search.yahoo.com/" title="Yahoo Search" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yahoo</a> or <a href="http://search.msn.com/" title="MSN Search" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MSN</a>.</li></ol><ol start="2"><li>I get 10 times more traffic from <a href="http://google.com/" title="Google" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google</a> than from <a href="http://search.yahoo.com/" title="Yahoo Search" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yahoo</a> or <a href="http://search.msn.com/" title="MSN Search" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MSN</a>.  </li></ol><h2 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h2><p>图片的语法和链接很像。<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![avatar](/pic/avatar.png &quot;头像&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><img src="/pic/avatar.png" alt="avatar" title="头像"></p><p>这里的avatar是当图片显示不出来的时候显示的文字，“头像”是图片下的文字，这两项都可以不填。</p><p>参考式的图片语法则长得像这样：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![Alt text][id]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[id]: /pic/avatar.png &quot;头像&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><hr><hr><hr><p>sublime中markdownlivepreview 的快捷方式是alt+m</p>]]></content>
    
